\section{Implementation}

\textbf{Backend}: Python 3.9+, FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, MySQL, ReportLab, Docker SDK.

\textbf{Frontend}: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind, Axios, Recharts.

\textbf{Key implementation choices}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Session token in \texttt{sessionStorage} for tab-level isolation (aligned with Chapter 3 constraints).
    \item Security logs normalized into \texttt{real} vs \texttt{challenge} context for cleaner analytics.
    \item Runtime schema guard in startup to add newly required columns when missing.
    \item Annotated diff generation for successful fix submissions integrated directly into frontend result modal.
\end{itemize}

